data.description: This low maintenance brick and vinyl {one owner} home is situated on a large corner lot in Southern Oaks. A wide foyer space welcomes you into a roomy living room with vaulted ceiling and fireplace. The kitchen boasts handsome stained cabinets, breakfast bar and an eat-in dining area. Primary bedroom has a tray ceiling and is spacious in size. Its bathroom has a double sink vanity, separate shower, jetted tub and two walk-in closets. Concrete patio is just off the living room and the back yard is fully fenced, perfect for entertaining and enjoying time outdoors. Double garage has convenient access to the back yard as well. Convenient to I-10 and easy access to major thoroughfares.   **SOLD AS-IS, the seller has not ever occupied the home.
